metadata.description:
it is the year 2525. a lot has happened and a lot will happen in the future. the apocalyptic worlds change the whole universe and the solar systems and leave the remaining residents with many questions unanswered: what's next? how can live in peace without fighting us and how will our existence continue... a story that will repeat itself again and again... the future is led by strong women with love, caution, foresight and sustainability...

Collection #1 of #25

every single collection consisting 25 unique items
